OL,5, A National Crime Agency (NCA) officer  
OL,6, who made offensive remarks about       
OL,7, Muslims was unfairly sacked, an        
OL,8, employment tribunal has found.         
OL,10,FAbbey Brooke made the comments at a    
OL,11,Ftraining session led by Abrar Javid, a 
OL,12,FMuslim community leader in Rotherham.  
OL,14,FThe tribunal said the intelligence     
OL,15,Fofficer's conduct had contributed to   
OL,16,Fher dismissal.                         
OL,18,FBut it found the dismissal was unfair  
OL,19,Fdue to procedural failures during the  
OL,20,FNCA disciplinary process.              
